{"tid":1720550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"發夢係埋大見到個好特別嘅手足 想大家一齊多謝佢","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:57:36.000Z","uid":33775,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a1a129115072a41f6b00322b7a251dbbc4329d","tid":1720550,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"執物資執到一半聽到有人問<br />\n有冇洗廁所用品呀<br />\n我聽完心諗邊個要呢d？整火魔呀？<br />\n點知一睇原來係一個中年阿姐 戴左個黑口罩就入黎幫手 佢可能冇乜野做到 所以想幫手足洗廁所<br />\n要知道而家個廁所係入去10秒都未必頂得順 因為用左黎倒酒 同埋有幾百條友一齊痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知佢最後搵唔搵到 但阿姐 向你致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有煮飯果班手足 好撚好食 （以呢個時勢黎講）起碼唔洗食腸仔先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcHUaZX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcHUaZX.png&h=725bc236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重申發夢見到 張相旅行影"},{"pid":"e1c16e63e6138a27ec06dadc32ce9d0595647632","tid":1720550,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69198cad2bce2796db5cb8406e2719cde1575b75","tid":1720550,"uid":3358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"去廁所真係去得乾淨d啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfb68e451e58a57e0fd7c727c7a063249ee6a30","tid":1720550,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69198cad2bce2796db5cb8406e2719cde1575b75","tid":1720550,"uid":3358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"去廁所真係去得乾淨d啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited